   <text>
      <body>
         <div subtype="1" type="letter">
            <pb n="1" facs="sc077a.small.jpg"/>
            <opener>
               <salute>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Dr</abbr>
                     <expan>Dear</expan>
                  </choice> Sir</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>I presume you have forgotten the Surgeonship of which I spoke to you on Sunday. If you will send me the name of any person you wish invited I will have the invitation sent to you, and will accompany it with such information in regard to the matter as will enable the person s invited to come to a just conclusion in regard to attending the Medical Boards.</p>
            <closer>
               <salute>
                  <choice>
                     <abbr>Respy</abbr>
                     <expan>Respectfully</expan>
                  </choice>
               </salute>
               <signed>
                  <name type="person">C A Harris</name>
               </signed>
               <add place="below signature">
                  <date when="--02-12">12 <choice>
                        <abbr>feby</abbr>
                        <expan>February</expan>
                     </choice>
                  </date>
               </add>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Hon</abbr>
                        <expan>Honorable</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <name type="person">
                        <choice>
                           <abbr> J K</abbr>
                           <expan>James Knox</expan>
                        </choice>  Polk</name>
                  </addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <unclear>Heofk</unclear>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
               <pb n="2" facs="sc077b.small.jpg"/>
               <address>
                  <addrLine>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>Hon</abbr>
                        <expan>Honorable</expan>
                     </choice>
                     <choice>
                        <abbr>J. K.</abbr>
                        <expan>James Knox</expan>
                     </choice> Polk</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>Speaker</addrLine>
                  <addrLine>
                     <unclear>Heofk</unclear>
                  </addrLine>
               </address>
